{
  "stem": "21310.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she was just praying not to fall off near there, because then we would know that, you know, she was-- fell off the train.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But-- and she had some-- quite some experiences.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And she finally she made it to Lwow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And a guard, an Ukrainian guard who was there, told her that he knew my aunt.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because she was very beloved there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "She was very good to-- anyway.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But she was-- that she was on that truck.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And when they were taking them out and she was yelling, it's all a mistake.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It's all a mistake.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I'm going-- somebody's coming to save me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It's all a mistake.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But they were all taken outside and they had to dig their own graves.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they were all shot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So that's one thing that, you know, I can never, never forget.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I still have that-- that picture of her at-- on that truck, halfway-- half out of her mind, you know, in fear, and yelling, somebody's coming to save me.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [SIGHS] I get-- well, [LAUGHS] I don't know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm talking so much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there was one-- one incident with a lot of chutzpah on my part.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I still don't know how I-- how I did it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One time, I was in Warsaw railroad station.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the trains-- I wanted to go to Otwock-- and the trains were full.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And no Poles could go in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had a book.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think it was [INAUDIBLE] or [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I forgot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In German.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I very frequently carried a German book with me, so as to pretend that I am German.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And as I said, I sometimes jumped on trolley cars, German trolley cars, if somebody was following me.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
